# Styling Conventions (Litho)

Goal: Keep visual consistency by reusing Litho styles, CSS, Tailwind utility classes, and motion patterns.

## Reuse First
- Reuse SCSS/CSS in `frontend/src/Assets/**` and classnames used by existing components.
- Reuse motion from `Functions/GlobalAnimations` and `framer-motion` props already present.
- Keep spacing/typography scales consistent with Litho sections.

## Tailwind & Classes
- Prefer existing Tailwind utilities and classes seen across pages; avoid inventing new spacing scales.
- Keep classlists terse and consistent; factor reusable class combinations into styled wrappers if repeated.

## Components & Layout
- Use existing Grid/Container/Row/Col from react-bootstrap as in Litho pages to maintain responsive breakpoints.
- For carousels, reuse Swiper configurations already present.

## Theming
- Respect existing color palette; introduce new tokens only when required and add them via tailwind.config if needed.

## Litho Styling Assets to Reuse
- **SCSS Variables**: `Assets/scss/variables.scss` - use existing color, font, and spacing variables
- **Mixins**: `Assets/scss/mixins.scss` - reuse responsive breakpoints and animations
- **Global Styles**: `Assets/scss/global.scss` - inherit typography and base styles
- **Component Styles**: Individual component SCSS files in `Assets/scss/components/`

## Motion & Animation Patterns
- **Framer Motion**: Reuse configurations from `Functions/GlobalAnimations.js`
- **Swiper**: Use existing carousel configurations from Litho pages
- **Hover Effects**: Reuse existing hover states and transitions

## Layout Patterns
- **Grid System**: Always use react-bootstrap's Container/Row/Col as in Litho
- **Spacing Scale**: Use Tailwind spacing utilities already present (py-[130px], mb-24, etc.)
- **Typography Scale**: Reuse existing heading classes (heading-4, heading-5, etc.)

## CSS Class Reuse Examples
```jsx
// Reuse existing button classes
<Buttons className="btn-fancy btn-fill font-medium font-serif rounded-none uppercase"
         themeColor="#232323" color="#fff" />

// Reuse existing section spacing
<section className="py-[130px] lg:py-[90px] md:py-[75px] sm:py-[50px]">
  {/* content */}
</section>

// Reuse existing carousel classes
<div className="swiper-pagination-light swiper-pagination-medium white-move">
  {/* swiper content */}
</div>
```

